element.name: mast hill by trackhead, Traditional Cache (1/2)
element.description: park at entrance to forest follow paths up to masts enjoy!!!
element.encoded-hints: hidden between small tree and fence

ul.li:
2010-06-05T19:00:00Z : Found it by Gruntplace
Nicely hidden. Great views

2010-05-29T19:00:00Z : Found it by BlueFoxPL
Another great day for caching... found with some friends. TFTC.

2010-05-29T19:00:00Z : Found it by Wicca Cailín
Stunning views, lovely little forest too. Lots of mountain bikers about as there seem to be tracks all around here. Did my impression of a lost tourist as they passed and then made a mad dash for the cache.[;)] TFTC
Out: Face fan flower In: Bouncing ball

2010-05-13T19:00:00Z : Found it by st5346
Found this one on my way along the coast in a 2 week vacation in Ireland! Very nice place, thanks for sharing this one!

2010-05-02T19:00:00Z : Found it by paddycacher
Found quite easily, Great view on the way back down.TNLN
